# SEO Page Rules

## Useful Content
Write direct, practical, operator-friendly language. Avoid fluffy deployment theory. Do not invent facts.

## Search Intent
Address the user's intent clearly and concisely. Format H1s properly (e.g., 'Audit Your [Workflow] Before Automating It With AI' for audit pages). Ensure descriptive H2s.

## FAQ/Schema
Include 4-6 FAQs per page. Include valid JSON-LD schema (Article and FAQPage).

## Internal Links
Maintain internal link structures based on directory depth. Maintain consistent navigation headers and footers across pages.

## No Thin Doorway Pages
Provide substantive value on every SEO page. No auto-generated low-value pages.
